uncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":69,"content":"**刀序铁律：** A → B → C → D → E → F → G。**禁止**跳步（例：未改 validate 就先全库锚点双轨；未 E1 就宣称 ASSET 校验可编）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":70,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":85,"content":"### 2.0 角色全局化（路径 B 铁律）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":86,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":87,"content":"| 项 | 口径 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":88,"content":"|----|------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":89,"content":"| 角色真源 | **仅** `data/characters/<agentId>.json` + `/api/characters` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":90,"content":"| 故事包不私有角色 | **禁止** `participants` 当白名单；作者不手维护 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":91,"content":"| 「本包用到谁」 | `cards[].ownerAgentId` + effects 内 `agentId` + attach 目标归属 **派生** |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":92,"content":"| 编辑器锚点 | **全库**显示；挂卡数来自本包 cards；未用可灰显 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":93,"content":"| 「添加角色」 | **仅**角色库新建；不是加入包 participants |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":94,"content":"| participants | 新包可不写；保存推荐不写；校验现场派生 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":95,"content":"| layout.lanes | Studio 按库序或「有卡者优先」派生；引擎忽略 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":96,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":97,"content":"### 2.1 引擎 validatePackage 改造","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":98,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":99,"content":"1. **`collectReferencedAgentIds(bundle)`**：扫描 ownerAgentId、effects.agentId、end_story.next.agentId、attach 目标归属等（与 validate 一致）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":100,"content":"2. **`REFERENCED_AGENT_UNKNOWN`**（error）：派生 id 不在角色库。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":101,"content":"3. **`validateParticipantsCharacters`** 对**派生集合**执行。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":102,"content":"4. **`PARTICIPANT_UNKNOWN`**：非空遗留 participants 未知 → **warning**「遗留字段将忽略」；空数组不报错。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":103,"content":"5. **ownerAgentId 不在旧 participants** 但在角色库 → 不得 error。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":104,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":105,"content":"### 2.2 包内卡生命周期（P0）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":106,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":107,"content":"| 操作 | 必须行为 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":108,"content":"|------|----------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":169,"content":"### 2.8 故事包列表与新建","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":170,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":171,"content":"| 项 | 口径 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":172,"content":"|----|------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":173,"content":"| 搜索 | filter title / packageId |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":174,"content":"| 新建 | `POST /api/stories` 最小 conf（可无 participants）+ layout + 可选默认 entry 卡 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":175,"content":"| 删除 mock | `commitCreatePackageMock` throw 清零 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":176,"content":"| characterCount | 派生「本包引用角色数」 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":177,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":178,"content":"### 2.9 角色库 / 玩家 UX","contentTruncated":false,