4721796930\",\"updatedAt\":\"1784721948092\",\"dependencies\":[]},{\"id\":\"3\",\"content\":\"确认 effect 下拉全库；补/改回归测试\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_COMPLETED\",\"createdAt\":\"1784721796930\",\"updatedAt\":\"1784721948092\",\"dependencies\":[]},{\"id\":\"4\",\"content\":\"跑 quality:engine + quality:studio；索引 ⬜→✅\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_COMPLETED\" [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":891,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-321f06df-c475-49f0-8608-0a48fe76dde0-95\\nfc_5a13ce30-7692-98e3-8b03-c473c66fd246_0\",\"tool_call\":{\"editToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_执行索引.md\",\"streamContent\":\"| ✅ | V2-S8-11 | **去 participants**：包配置只读派生；lanes 派生；characterCount 派生；effect 源全库 | npm run quality:studio |\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_执行索引.md\",\"linesAdded\":1,\"linesRemoved\":1,\"diffString\":\"--- a//Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_执行索引.md\\n+++ b//Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_执行索引.md\\n@@ -166,7 +166,7 @@\\n | ✅ | V2-S8-8 | **condition 写盘**：写 exit.condition；summary 派生；requiredBeats 供 beatId 下拉；禁止 DEFAULT 覆盖已有 condition | npm run quality:studio |\\n | ✅ | V2-S8-9 | **出口 roundtrip**：exitKind/priority/condition 单测；callCardProjectionMapper 不再丢 condition/critical | npm run quality:studio |\\n | [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":894,"content":"{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"**V2-S8-11 已完成**（去 participants 双轨）。\\n\\n### 实现要点\\n- 新增 `referencedAgentsDerive.ts`：用引擎 `collectReferencedAgentIds` 派生本包引用角色\\n- **包配置**：只读展示派生引用（非白名单）；`wrong_number_act1` → `lanxing`\\n- **lanes**：保存/缺省 layout 按派生引用写入；引擎仍忽略\\n- **characterCount**：列表扫描读 cards 后派生（act1 = 1）\\n- **保存**：磁盘 omit `participants` 键；会话内清空为 `[]`\\n- **Effect 下拉**：沿用全库锚点；补回归测\\n\\n### Verify\\n- `npm run quality:engine` → ok  \\n- `npm run quality:studio` → ok  \\n\\n执行索引 **V2-S8-11** 已 ⬜→✅。\"}]},\"session_id\":\"b3f16bdc-d809-4891-a7df-372622951939\"}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":896,"content":"{\"type\":\"result\",\"subtype\":\"success\",\"duration_ms\":276210,\"duration_api_ms\":276210,\"is_error\":false,\"result\":\"先读取指定的 prompt 文件，并按其要求逐步执行。按 prompt 要求，先读执行索引与相关需求，确认 V2-S8-11 的具体范围。继续读取任务详情与相关代码现状。对照需求，继续排查仍依赖 `participants` 的代码路径。继续核对保存写盘、包列表与测试中仍依赖 `participants` 的路径。开始实现：先核对 `wrong_number_act1` 的引用角色，再改派生逻辑。开始落地代码改动。修正写盘逻辑：内存保留完整 conf，磁盘省略 `participants`。`quality:engine` 已通过，接着跑 `quality:studio`。修复类型：会话内清空 `participants`，磁盘写时再省略该键。`package/graph` 触发目录聚类门禁；把派生逻辑移到 `package/conf/`。两项 verify 已通过，正在把执行索引中的 V2-S8-11 标为 ✅。**V2-S8-11 已完成**（去 participants 双轨）。\\n\\n### 实现要点\\n- 新增 `referencedAgentsDerive.ts`：用引擎 `collectReferencedAgentIds` 派生本包引用角色\\n- **包配置**：只读展示派生引用（非白名单）；`wrong_number_act1` → `lanxing`\\n- **lanes**：保存/缺省 layout 按派生引用写入；引擎仍忽略\\n- **characterCount**：列表扫描读 cards 后派生（act1 = 1）\\n- **保存**：磁盘 omit `participants` 键；会话内清空为 `[]`\\n- **Effect 下拉**：沿用全库锚点；补回归测\\n\\n### Verify\\n- `npm run quality:engine` → ok  \\n- `npm run quality:studio` → ok  \\n\\n执行索引 **V2-S8-11** 已 ⬜→✅。\",\"session_id\":\"b3f1 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":897,"content":"先读取指定的 prompt 文件，并按其要求逐步执行。按 prompt 要求，先读执行索引与相关需求，确认 V2-S8-11 的具体范围。继续读取任务详情与相关代码现状。对照需求，继续排查仍依赖 `participants` 的代码路径。继续核对保存写盘、包列表与测试中仍依赖 `participants` 的路径。开始实现：先核对 `wrong_number_act1` 的引用角色，再改派生逻辑。开始落地代码改动。修正写盘逻辑：内存保留完整 conf，磁盘省略 `participants`。`quality:engine` 已通过，接着跑 `quality:studio`。修复类型：会话内清空 `participants`，磁盘写时再省略该键。`package/graph` 触发目录聚类门禁；把派生逻辑移到 `package/conf/`。两项 verify 已通过，正在把执行索引中的 V2-S8-11 标为 ✅。**V2-S8-11 已完成**（去 participants 双轨）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":908,"content